      Classes in ex2 that implement Energy 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AggressiveShip
      The Class represent an Aggressive ship, trying to fly after the nearest ship and if it answer the precautions warning it will fire!
      class  BasherShip
      The Class represent a Basher ship, trying to fly after the nearest ship and if it answer the precautions warning it will put the shield on!
      class  DrunkaedShip
      The Class represent an Drunkard ship, flying like there is a drunkard pilot in it and randomly shoot or teleport.
      class  EnemyShip
      The Class represent an abstract enemy ship (means not human controlled).
      class  HumanControlledShip
      Class charge on HumanControlled ship, the pilot can to what ever he likes to!
      class  RunnerShip
      Class that charge on Runner ship - always trying to avoid facing fight.
      class  SpaceShip
      Class represent the abstract SpaceShip in the game.
      class  SpecialShip
      Class that charge on Special ship -In start it looks like very easy pilot to kill but then it's attack with all the power be ready!.
